AV Monitoring is a availability monitoring system, which provide 
an interval TCP socket check to the server for a binary status 
“online” and “offline”, and alert report to system admin via E-Mail,
record to Google Calendar and sent SMS (with Google Calendar service). 
AV Monitoring provide 2 reports; status report for each servers 
each services and amount of downtime.

